INSERT INTO `lc_draw` (`id`, `invest`, `invite`, `register`, `upgrade`, `point`, `content_zh_cn`, `content_zh_hk`, `content_en_us`, `content_th_th`, `content_vi_vn`, `content_ja_jp`, `content_ko_kr`, `content_ms_my`, `content_pt_pt`, `content_es_es`, `content_tr_tr`, `content_id_id`, `content_de_de`, `content_fr_fr`) VALUES (1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 20, '<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\">1、邀请好友赠送1次抽奖次数</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\">2、注册赠送1次抽奖次数</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\">3、投资成功赠送1次抽奖次数</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\">4、抽中现金直接返现到资金账户</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\">5、抽中实物，请及时联系在线客服提供收件人信息，平台会在30天内安排发货</span></span></p>\r\n', '<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>1、邀請好友贈送1次抽獎次數</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>2、註冊贈送1次抽獎次數</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>3、投資成功贈送1次抽獎次數</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>4、抽中現金直接返現到資金賬戶</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>5、抽中實物，請及時聯繫在線客服提供收件人信息，平台會在30天內安排發貨</strong></span></p>\r\n', '<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>1. Invite friends to give away the number of draws once</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>2. The number of draws of registered gifts</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>3. The number of draws successfully for investment</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>4. Cash cash will be cash directly to the fund account</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>5. Pick up the physical object, please contact the online customer service in time to provide the recipient information. The platform will arrange delivery within 30 days</strong></span></p>\r\n', '<p><strong><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\">1. เชิญเพื่อนมาให้จำนวนการจับรางวัลครั้งเดียว</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\">2. จำนวนของขวัญที่ลงทะเบียน</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\">3. จำนวนการดึงที่ประสบความสำเร็จในการลงทุน</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\">4. เงินสดเงินสดจะเป็นเงินสดโดยตรงไปยังบัญชีกองทุน</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\">5. รับวัตถุทางกายภาพโปรดติดต่อฝ่ายบริการลูกค้าออนไลน์ทันเวลาเพื่อให้ข้อมูลผู้รับแพลตฟอร์มจะจัดส่งภายใน 30 วัน</span></strong></p>\r\n', '<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>1. Mời bạn b&egrave; cho đi số lượng trận h&ograve;a một lần</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>2. Số lượng c&aacute;c m&oacute;n qu&agrave; đ&atilde; đăng k&yacute;</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>3. Số lượng r&uacute;t thăm th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng cho đầu tư</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>4. Tiền mặt sẽ trực tiếp bằng tiền mặt v&agrave;o t&agrave;i khoản quỹ</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>5. Nhận đối tượng vật l&yacute;, vui l&ograve;ng li&ecirc;n hệ với dịch vụ kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng trực tuyến kịp thời để cung cấp th&ocirc;ng tin người nhận. Nền tảng sẽ sắp xếp giao h&agrave;ng trong v&ograve;ng 30 ng&agrave;y</strong></span></p>\r\n', '<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>1.友達を招待して、一度引き分けの数を渡してください</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>2.登録ギフトの引き分けの数</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>3.投資のための引き分けの数</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>4.現金現金はファンドアカウントに直接現金になります</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>5.物理的なオブジェクトをピックアップして、オンラインカスタマーサービスに間に合わせて受信者情報を提供してください。プラットフォームは30日以内に配達を手配します</strong></span></p>\r\n', '<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>1. 친구를 초대하여 무승부 횟수를 한 번 제공하십시오.</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>2. 등록 된 선물의 추첨 수</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>3. 투자를 위해 성공적으로 추첨을합니다</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>4. 현금 현금은 펀드 계좌로 직접 현금이됩니다.</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>5. 물리적 개체를 선택하십시오. 수신자 정보를 제공하려면 온라인 고객 서비스에 연락하십시오. 플랫폼은 30 일 이내에 배송을 준비합니다.</strong></span></p>\r\n', '<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>1. Jemput rakan untuk memberikan jumlah cabutan sekali</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>2. Bilangan cabutan hadiah berdaftar</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>3. Bilangan cabutan berjaya untuk pelaburan</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>4. Tunai tunai akan tunai terus ke akaun dana</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>5. Ambil objek fizikal, sila hubungi perkhidmatan pelanggan dalam talian pada waktunya untuk memberikan maklumat penerima. Platform akan mengatur penghantaran dalam masa 30 hari</strong></span></p>\r\n', '<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>1. Convide amigos para doar o n&uacute;mero de empates uma vez</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>2. O n&uacute;mero de sorteios de presentes registrados</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>3. O n&uacute;mero de sorteios com sucesso para investimento</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>4. Caixa em dinheiro ser&aacute; dinheiro diretamente para a conta do fundo</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>5. Pegue o objeto f&iacute;sico, entre em contato com o atendimento ao cliente on -line a tempo de fornecer as informa&ccedil;&otilde;es do destinat&aacute;rio. A plataforma organizar&aacute; a entrega dentro de 30 dias</strong></span></p>\r\n', '<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>1. Invite a sus amigos a regalar el n&uacute;mero de sorteos una vez</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>2. La cantidad de sorteos de regalos registrados</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>3. El n&uacute;mero de sorteos con &eacute;xito para la inversi&oacute;n</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>4. El efectivo en efectivo ser&aacute; efectivo directamente a la cuenta del fondo</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>5. Recoja el objeto f&iacute;sico, comun&iacute;quese con el servicio al cliente en l&iacute;nea a tiempo para proporcionar la informaci&oacute;n del destinatario. La plataforma organizar&aacute; la entrega dentro de los 30 d&iacute;as</strong></span></p>\r\n', '<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>1. Arkadaşları bir kez &ccedil;ekiliş sayısını vermeye davet edin</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>2. Kayıtlı Hediyelerin &Ccedil;ekme Sayısı</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>3. Yatırım i&ccedil;in başarılı bir şekilde &ccedil;ekiliş sayısı</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>4. Nakit nakit doğrudan fon hesabına nakit olacaktır</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>5. Fiziksel nesneyi alın, alıcı bilgilerini sağlamak i&ccedil;in l&uuml;tfen &ccedil;evrimi&ccedil;i m&uuml;şteri hizmetiyle iletişime ge&ccedil;in. Platform, teslimatı 30 g&uuml;n i&ccedil;inde d&uuml;zenleyecektir.</strong></span></p>\r\n', '<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>1. Laden Sie Freunde ein, die Anzahl der Ziehungen einmal zu verschenken</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>2. Die Anzahl der Unentschieden von registrierten Geschenken</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>3. Die Anzahl der erfolgreichsten Ziehungen f&uuml;r Investitionen</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>4. Bargeld ist Bargeld direkt auf das Fondskonto sein</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>5. Nehmen Sie das physische Objekt ab, wenden Sie sich rechtzeitig an den Online -Kundendienst, um die Empf&auml;ngerinformationen bereitzustellen. Die Plattform arrangiert die Lieferung innerhalb von 30 Tagen</strong></span></p>\r\n', '<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>1. Laden Sie Freunde ein, die Anzahl der Ziehungen einmal zu verschenken</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>2. Die Anzahl der Unentschieden von registrierten Geschenken</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>3. Die Anzahl der erfolgreichsten Ziehungen f&uuml;r Investitionen</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>4. Bargeld ist Bargeld direkt auf das Fondskonto sein</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>5. Nehmen Sie das physische Objekt ab, wenden Sie sich rechtzeitig an den Online -Kundendienst, um die Empf&auml;ngerinformationen bereitzustellen. Die Plattform arrangiert die Lieferung innerhalb von 30 Tagen</strong></span></p>\r\n', '<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>1. Invitez des amis &agrave; donner le nombre de tirages une fois</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>2. Le nombre de tirages de cadeaux enregistr&eacute;s</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>3. Le nombre de tirages avec succ&egrave;s pour l&#39;investissement</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>4. L&#39;esp&egrave;ces en esp&egrave;ces sera directement en esp&egrave;ces sur le compte de fonds</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ecf0f1;\"><strong>5. Procurez-vous l&#39;objet physique, veuillez contacter le service client en ligne &agrave; temps pour fournir les informations du destinataire. La plate-forme organisera la livraison dans les 30 jours</strong></span></p>\r\n');
